[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/System Requirements]]
The basic system requirements for playing OpenTTD are as follows:

==All Operating Systems==
OpenTTD requires a [[en/Archive/Manual/Installation FAQ|few files]] from either the DOS or Windows version of the original Transport Tycoon Deluxe.  Note that Transport Tycoon is a earlier game and not compatible.

==Windows== 

*Windows 95/98/ME/2000/XP
*Minimum 233MHz or above computer (500MHz+ for reasonable play, 1GHz+ recommended)
*64Mb RAM (128Mb+ recommended)
*DirectX 7 or above
*10Mb free hard disk space (not including savegames and screenshots. 50Mb recommended)

==Linux== 
*Linux 2.2 or above (?)
*Minimum 233MHz or above computer (500MHz+ for reasonable play, 1GHz+ recommended)
*SDL supported graphics card (?)
*64Mb RAM (128Mb+ recommended)
*10Mb free hard disk space (not including savegames and screenshots. 50Mb recommended)

